# NBT-003 — Claim Control Register

Version: v1_1 governance build  
Date: 2026-06-24

| Term / Claim family | Allowed wording | Conditional wording | Prohibited wording | Current status |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| TPW | discrete probability-simplex framework | finite product-measure simplex model | universal physical law | ALLOWED |
| Raphael Equations | equation-register and correspondence scaffold | proposed operators requiring audit | proven field equations | CONDITIONAL |
| Gravity well | gravity-well analogy / log-density well | potential-like visualization after definition | physical gravity equivalence | ANALOGY ONLY |
| Entropy hub | simplex entropy maximum under stated constraints | modal/entropy relation if formally proven | hub is uniquely proven universal attractor | OPEN |
| Spiral | imposed traversal / visualization | intrinsic spiral if invariant theorem proven | necessary natural spiral law | VISUALIZATION ONLY |
| Pilot wave | pilot-wave-inspired rendering | predictive pilot-wave method after backtesting | proven pilot-wave predictor | UNVALIDATED |
| N-body | finite N-variable product-measure schema | physical N-body correspondence after mechanics proof | universal N-body mechanics | CONDITIONAL |
| MMB / non-locality | hypothesis / observer aggregation model | formal information-theoretic theorem if proven | proof of non-local realism | HYPOTHESIS |
| Scale-free isomorphism | structural analogy | isomorphism after bijection and preservation proofs | proven scale-free physical isomorphism | UNPROVEN |
| ToE | not used in proof text | aspirational research context only | Theory of Everything proven | PROHIBITED |

## Replacement phrasing

Use:

```text
mathematical correspondence
visual analogy
finite product-measure generalization
controlled hypothesis
requires dimensional and empirical validation
```

Avoid:

```text
proves physics
unifies all fields
quantum gravity solved
validated ToE
```
